N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4025.41 - When entry is void

State Regulations

If the produce of a mare is dropped before January
1st, or if there is no produce, or if the produce is dead when dropped, of if
twins are dropped, the entry of such mare is void. Notes
